{"tid":1498909,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］陳帆：政府非常關注有人發起明日不同方式妨礙機場運作","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:04:17.000Z","uid":199926,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c7a813440f1f26a6c0f091b4c15b8d5bed5763","tid":1498909,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"政府舉行跨門記者會，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，本月9日至13日期間在機場的公眾集會嚴重影響機場運作，導致近1000班航班取消，對大量旅客造成不便和人身安全影響。香港機場本月首21日的客運量是416萬人次，較去年同期下跌超過11%，即減少54萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆說，留意到網上有人發起明天以不同方式妨礙機場運作，例如故意堵塞前往機場的道路，政府非常關注事件，會密切留意。他強調，機管局已獲法庭批准延長臨時禁制令，禁制令是禁止任何人阻礙機場正常使用或阻礙機場附近的道路，可被控藐視法庭，協助他人違反禁制令亦可被控藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆說，有傳聞指有示威者透過租用旅遊巴、的士或出租車，意圖堵塞前往機場的路道，他提醒司機，若協助他人違反禁制令亦可能被控藐視法庭。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476370-20190823.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476370-20190823.htm&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAiRJil42CLA7NmQUB0MJ4tY%3D&h=bbf41530\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476370-20190823.htm&h=37946cff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476370-20190823.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5651068ffadccb8a621b22d754ad7e5de4832002","tid":1498909,"uid":199926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>做對了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bb64f02163684ff74cb2213fcfd41b4bf3ee3a90","tid":1498909,"uid":199926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:24:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvBNzCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdvBNzCN.jpg&h=b8dbf679&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb5bcf1ba2102e8f02f2cf4e99c8c8850c56bcc","tid":1498909,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-